descriptionHtml:
The Mastery Charter Schools app provides a simple and secure way to keep informed of all things Mastery Charter Schools related. It is a safe way for parents and educators to connect. With this app you’ll be able to:

** Stay up-to-date on the latest Mastery Charter Schools News and Announcement
** View upcoming events
** View all district, school and classroom communication and receive app notifications
** Send direct messages to your teachers
** View photos and videos posted by teachers
** Fill forms online and sign permission slips
** Sign up for parent teacher conferences
** View the school and classroom calendar and RSVP for events
** Easily sign up to volunteer and/or bring items
** View notices (attendance, cafeteria, library dues)
** Respond to absences
** Purchase goods and services offered for sale by your school, pay invoices
descriptionShort: A private and secure communication platform for Mastery Charter Schools.
